Submit Bugs for Feature Requests
================================

Visit <https://gitlab.com/Nanolx/bashstyle-ng/issues> for reporting
bugs.

   Please make sure that you got the latest stable version of
BashStyle-NG.  If you got an Feature Request or a new Idea for
BashStyle-NG, don't hesitate to post it!  If you can provide patches,
then that's even better.
